1375
01:42:46.734 --> 01:42:48.502
He might look like
Voldemort's nut sack.

1376
01:42:48.636 --> 01:42:51.338
but trust me. we're gonna
need this fucker.

1377
01:42:52.472 --> 01:42:55.743
Hey. g'day. Blondie.
Long time no see.

1378
01:42:56.844 --> 01:42:58.579
You ready
for your next lesson?

1379
01:42:58.713 --> 01:43:01.783
For the glory
of Johnny Fucking Cage.

1380
01:43:02.517 --> 01:43:04.484
[Baraka grunts]

1381
01:43:04.619 --> 01:43:07.588
Let's go get our friends.
Then we kill Kano.

1382
